WWW-Scraper-ISBN-Pearson_Driver
===============================

This module is a Perl extension for ISBN search collection that is provide by
WWW::Scraper::ISBN.

This driver searches for book information from the Pearson Education online 
catalog.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules:

  WWW::Scraper::ISBN
  WWW::Scraper::ISBN::Record
  WWW::Scraper::ISBN::Driver
  WWW::Mechanize

For optional testing the module would like these other modules:

  Test::Pod
  Test::Pod::Coverage
  Test::CPAN::Meta
  Test::CPAN::Meta::JSON

